instruction: Create a new story using the provided characters and setting.
input: Characters: Alfie, Lucy and Mark; Setting: a magical forest
output: Alfie, Lucy and Mark ventured into a magical forest in search of a hidden treasure. But what they found was far beyond their wildest imaginations - they stumbled upon two fairy kingdoms located in two different parts of the forest. Alfie was determined to find out what the treasure was, while Lucy and Mark were more interested in exploring the mysterious kingdoms. With determination and courage, the trio managed to complete their mission and found the hidden treasure, a magical artifact that granted them all the wishes they ever wanted.
